#. <section class="sutta" id="sn47.27"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn47.27:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 47"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 47"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn47.27:0.2"
msgid "3. Sīlaṭṭhitivagga"
msgstr "3. Ethics and Duration"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn47.27:0.3"
msgid "27. Samattasutta"
msgstr "27. Completely"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn47.27:1.1"
msgid "Taṃyeva nidānaṃ."
msgstr "The same setting."

msgctxt "sn47.27:1.2"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho āyasmā sāriputto āyasmantaṃ anuruddhaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn47.27:1.3"
msgid "“‘asekho, asekho’ti, āvuso anuruddha, vuccati."
msgstr "“Reverend, they speak of this person called ‘an adept’."

msgctxt "sn47.27:1.4"
msgid "Kittāvatā nu kho, āvuso, asekho hotī”ti?"
msgstr "How is an adept defined?”"

msgctxt "sn47.27:1.5"
msgid "“Catunnaṃ kho, āvuso, satipaṭṭhānānaṃ samattaṃ bhāvitattā asekho hoti."
msgstr ""
"“Reverends, an adept is someone who has completely developed the four kinds "
"of mindfulness meditation."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn47.27:2.1"
msgid "Katamesaṃ catunnaṃ?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "sn47.27:2.2"
msgid ""
"Idhāvuso, bhikkhu kāye kāyānupassī viharati ātāpī sampajāno satimā, vineyya "
"loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ;"
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant meditates by observing an aspect of the body—keen, "
"aware, and mindful, rid of desire and aversion for the world."

msgctxt "sn47.27:2.3"
msgid "vedanāsu … pe …"
msgstr "They meditate observing an aspect of feelings …"

msgctxt "sn47.27:2.4"
msgid "citte … pe …"
msgstr "mind …"

msgctxt "sn47.27:2.5"
msgid ""
"dhammesu dhammānupassī viharati ātāpī sampajāno satimā, vineyya loke "
"abhijjhādomanassaṃ."
msgstr ""
"principles—keen, aware, and mindful, rid of desire and aversion for the "
"world."

msgctxt "sn47.27:2.6"
msgid ""
"Imesaṃ kho, āvuso, catunnaṃ satipaṭṭhānānaṃ samattaṃ bhāvitattā asekho "
"hotī”ti."
msgstr ""
"An adept is someone who has completely developed the four kinds of "
"mindfulness meditation.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn47.27:2.7"
msgid "Sattamaṃ."
msgstr ""
